text = "[b]Project[/b]
- A Day in the Life
- Interactive experience created for the assignment:
  \"A Day in the Life of a First Year Game Design Student\"
- Developed in Godot.

[b]Sound[/b]
- Home / Morning Routine Level:
   \"Lo Fi Hip Hop (Cozy Morning)\"
   by Alex_Kizenkov
   Source: Pixabay

- Main Menu / Calm Background Music:
  \"Morning Lofi Chill Music\"
  by SoundGalleryByDmitryTaras
  Source: Pixabay

- Parkour / Travelling to University Level:
   \"Game Background Loop – Uplifting Adventure Music Loop\"
   by Cyberwave-Orchestra
   Source: Pixabay

[b]Environment Asset[/b]
- Furniture Kit by Kenney.
- Used for 3D environment/furniture assets in the project.
- License: Creative Commons CC0 / Public Domain.
- Source: https://www.kenney.nl/assets/furniture-kit
